Skills.Name: Battle Command
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of single ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Also raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s. Further raises CRIT ATK by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 10s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP, raises ATK of single ally, raises CRIT ATK if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: On Target
Skills.Description: Inflicts Dark on single enemy with highest ATK for 10s. Further lowers DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Dark, lowers DEF of single enemy
